---
title: Classic Chicken Burger with Beetroot Relish & Fries
description: Bring a little flair to burger night by using classic flavours such as beetroot relish, Aussie spice blend and dill-parsley mayo to turn
a tender chicken fillet into a filling supreme burger.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/classic-chicken-burger-d3c87813.jpg
